description: An intelligent and highly motivated individual, who works in a creative field but pursued academics at Harvard as a secondary passion. She lives away from the friends and family around whom she grew up. Digital media classes have her considering a career switch.
undergraduate_comment: At a local specialised college. Studied applied design, which quickly turned into a career.
highschool_comment: Local high school doing honors level course work. Highly motivated, a high achiever. Participated in a few academic clubs.
digitalmedia: Currently uses online tutorials and/or discussion boards to learn digital media. Sometimes signs up for digital conferences to experience the community more, but may not fully participate. Talks primarily to professors for any advice related to field. Googles the rest.
goals: Meet like-minded people  Get help / level-up skills Step out of current profession
hobbies: Coffee • Travelling • Tennis • Cooking • Art & Architecture
frustration: Lacks network in Digital Media  Too many tools (Fb groups, slacks etc)
worklife: Mid level position, managing a small team (2-3) of juniors.
